general.gigTitle: design, develop and customize a responsive wordpress website

sellerCard.oneLiner: Expert on Shopify, WordPress, Wix, PHP , HTML, CSS and Databases
sellerCard.description: Welcome! I am a Experienced Web Designer & Developer, Graphics Designer. I specialize in developing and marketing superior quality professional Wordpress, Shopify, Wix and custom websites for my clients. I'm able to create a website that won't just suit your requirements, but also take care of your budget.

description.content:
Hi, Im DABEER, I am Experience WordPress developer with over 5 years of experience. Im able to make own Custom-Designs and templates, mobile responsive and SEO Friendly 

 

Let me help you create or improve your online presence.  

Each business is different, and I will make sure that your WordPress site is designed specifically for your target audience. 

 

What is included in this gig? 

 

  • A Complete WordPress Setup 
  • Professional High-End Design 
  • Responsive Across All Devices & Browsers 
  • SEO Friendly 
  • Woo Commerce Setup 
  • Payment gateway 
  • Contact Form 
  • Live Chatbot (if needed) 
  • Fast Loading 
  • Site Map 
  • Google Site Kit. 
  • Free Security & Backup Plugins included 

 

 

100% satisfaction is guaranteed. Plus, 3 FREE Revisions are included with every package. 

If you have any special requirements or have questions, drop me a message. Please contact me before placing an order as I like to discuss before taking a Website project that helps both of us to avoid order cancellation.  

 

 

 

THANK YOU. 

DABEER

questionsAndAnswers.question: Why is it compulsory to contact first before ordering?
questionsAndAnswers.answer: Because we can discuss the availability, cost, and delivery time of a project and other feasibilities. Every job is different and needs a specific amount of time, dedication, and commitment so, kindly contact me before ordering.

questionsAndAnswers.question: What are the requirements for creating a WordPress site?
questionsAndAnswers.answer: You need to have a domain and a cPanel based hosting account that supports WordPress installation (e.g. Goddady or Wpengine). If you don't have a domain or hosting yet, I will be happy to assist you. I will also need your logo, content, e-mail address to configure contact form.

questionsAndAnswers.question: How long will it take to build your website?
questionsAndAnswers.answer: BASIC PACKAGE websites takes approximately 24 hours (1 Days) to create. Sites with Online store, News Portals, and websites with many elements takes some time its better to contact me before place an order.

questionsAndAnswers.question: I like some websites very much , can you create something similar?
questionsAndAnswers.answer: Well, I can answer this question after checking the website. You are highly welcome to share your ideas and thought in the inbox, thank you.

questionsAndAnswers.question: Can you help me write content for my website?
questionsAndAnswers.answer: I can guide you through what kind of content helps leverage fantastic websites. Also you can search on this platform, Fiverr has many talented writers.

questionsAndAnswers.question: Do you provide any support after the site is launched?
questionsAndAnswers.answer: Yes, I offer 30-day post-sales support, but you can contact me even after the one month has passed. I am always here to help :)

questionsAndAnswers.question: Will I be able to edit my WordPress site?
questionsAndAnswers.answer: Yes, absolutely :) Your website will be fully editable. No programming skills required. I will also guide you how to edit pages, contents, images etc.
